OL,3,CMan dies in a crash after being chased
OL,4,Cby police in Hartlepool
OL,6,FA 44-year-old man has died in a
OL,7,Fcollision in Hartlepool after being
OL,8,Fchased by police.
OL,10,FDetectives say a blue VW Golf collided
OL,11,Fwith a concrete bollard on Tuesday 7
OL,12,FApril after being involved in a short
OL,13,Fpolice pursuit on Elizabeth Way.
OL,15,FThe driver died and two passengers in
OL,16,Fthe vehicle were taken to hospital; a
OL,17,F34-year-old man with serious injuries
OL,18,Fand a 42-year-old woman.
