OL,3,CMan dies in a crash after being chased
OL,4,Cby police in Hartlepool
OL,6,FCleveland Police has referred itself
OL,7,Fto the Independent Office for Police
OL,8,FConduct.
OL,10,FChief Inspector Zoe Kelsey said: "The
OL,11,Fblue VW Golf collided with a concrete
OL,12,Fbollard during the single vehicle
OL,13,Fcollision shortly after 4am, following
OL,14,Fa short pursuit.
OL,16,F"Due to the circumstances of the
OL,17,Fincident, the force has made a
OL,18,Fmandatory referral to the Independent
OL,19,FOffice for Police Conduct (IOPC)."
